Class ResultUsePolicyEvaluator<C, S, M extends S>

java.lang.Object
com.google.errorprone.bugpatterns.checkreturnvalue.ResultUsePolicyEvaluator<C,S,M>
Type Parameters:
C - the type of the context object used during evaluation
S - the type of symbols
M - the type of method symbols
public final class ResultUsePolicyEvaluator<C, S, M extends S> extends Object
Evaluates methods and their enclosing classes and packages to determine a ResultUsePolicy for the methods.
